{
  "stem": "25639.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you see, I had my loving mother and sister to live for, that hardly anybody else had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I decided to make the jump.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Then, in the middle of that night, I just made my way up to the roadside from where I jumped originally.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, it was war time, and there was a complete blackout observed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But a little light managed to seep through here and there from the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, I was limited by the electric wire fences.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know what was in this barrack where the little-- little light shone through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was just a tiny little light, much like a little star in the distance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I decided to just follow this little light.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It could have been a man's camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It could have been the SS headquarters-- I wouldn't have known.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But instead, I thank God provided me with a women's barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, these women were transferred there the previous day, and they were going to be shipped out to another camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were waiting for the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I entered this barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was no sentry in front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just was able to enter it, and I could see the-- the foot of the first bunk bed, and I headed toward that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I quickly climbed up to the top, and suddenly, somebody started to scream.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I could see that she will put me in danger, so I quickly cupped my hand on my mouth to indicate to her not to give me away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I explained to her my predicament.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She took off her men's overcoat and put it around me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She slept in it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that night, she took an overcoat off of a dead body.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
